links: Stephen A. Silver, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..255
Index entries for sequences related to enumerating groups.
prog: (GAP) A034383 := function(n) local fn, sum, k; fn := Factorial(n); sum := 0; for k in [1 .. NrSmallGroups(n)] do sum := sum + fn / Size(AutomorphismGroup(SmallGroup(n,k))); od; return sum; end; # _Stephen A. Silver_, Feb 10 2013
